document: Course materials not loading correctly during lectures; requested re-upload before next session.
Multiple lectures lacked sufficient examples; requested additional reference code and real-world use cases.
Lecture recordings not accessible after upload; requested faster content updates and reliable system synchronization.
Cloud Computing labs caused multiple login failures; escalation needed to restore student access.
Feedback delayed for more than two weeks despite follow-ups; requested process audit and instructor availability review.
Lecture materials were disorganized; slides missing and references outdated reported for revision.
Session scheduling conflicts caused missed attendance; requested calendar synchronization and faculty notice.
Database Systems evaluation rubric unclear; requested clarification from academic board before grading completion.
Assessment results published with missing entries; raised issue with registrar for verification.
Machine Learning project submission portal repeatedly timed out; requested system maintenance for stability.
Course evaluation survey not registering responses; issue escalated to IT for urgent review.
